title: Zuckerberg says Facebook's failure to remove militia page an 'operational mistake'
text: Facebook Inc made an "operational mistake" in not acting sooner to remove a page for a militia group that posted a call to arms in Kenosha, Wisconsin, the company's Chief Executive Mark Zuckerberg said on Friday.
